---
title: Grilled Thai-Spiced Salmon with Cucumber Salsa and Sweet Chili Glaze
description: Crunchy lime-pickled cucumbers and smoky grilled fish are the star of this super simple recipe that's packed with fresh and aromatic flavours!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saumon-grille-aux-epices-thaies-6b4ca16f.jpg
